						               													<description>In Heroescraft, you are the governor of one of the cities of the legendary land of Nidawellir. Mighty heroes are at your service, with whose tactical use you expand the economic influence of your city. Command your heroes skillfully and erect magnificent buildings that will give you both power and fame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this exciting, interactive economic strategy game, two to four players compete for supremacy in the region. With clever actions, the players try to get useful resources to expand their cities - often at the expense of their neighbors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Recognizing the plans of your competitors and thwarting them at the right time for your own benefit - therein lies the key to success in Heroescraft!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Because only those who make the best use of the skills of the heroes and the special privileges of the buildings will win the gripping competition for raw materials, reputation and power!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In order to win, the players must erect a certain number of buildings. Buildings are built by giving up certain raw materials. Raw materials can either be bought in the cities adjacent to the caravan. Or they can be exchanged with the players or with the bank through different heroes. When buying raw materials, the dynamic prices in the market must be taken into account.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
